BUX, Appellant, v. TIGHE, Respondent. (Supreme Court, Appellate Division, Second Department. June 22, 1906.)

In the matter of the application of Philip Bux for a peremp- *1109tory writ of mandamus against James G. Tighe, as magistrate, etc. No opinion. Order affirmed, with $10 costs and disbursements.
